#: ../../source/course_reserves.rst:6
msgid "Course reserves"
msgstr "课程预留"

#: ../../source/course_reserves.rst:8
msgid "The course reserves module in Koha allows you to temporarily move items to 'reserve' and assign different circulation rules to these items while they are being used for a specific course."
msgstr "Koha 的课程预留模块允许您暂时将文献移入‘预留’，并且使用特殊流通规则以便于上课时使用。"

#: ../../source/course_reserves.rst:15
msgid "Course reserves setup"
msgstr "课程预留设置"

#: ../../source/course_reserves.rst:17
msgid "Before using course reserves you will need to do some set up."
msgstr "使用课程预留前需要做一些设置。"

#: ../../source/course_reserves.rst:19
msgid "First you will need to enable course reserves by setting the :ref:`UseCourseReserves` preference to 'Use'."
msgstr "首先应当通过设置 :ref:`UseCourseReserves` 为‘使用’来启用课程预留。"

#: ../../source/course_reserves.rst:22
msgid "Next you will need to have all of your course instructors :ref:`added as patrons <add-a-new-patron-label>`."
msgstr "然后您需要将所有该课程的老师设置 :ref:`新增 <add-a-new-patron-label>`。"

#: ../../source/course_reserves.rst:25
msgid "Next you will want to add a couple of new :ref:`authorized values <add-new-authorized-value-label>` for Departments and Terms."
msgstr "接下来您需要新增一些院系和学期的 :ref:`规范值 <add-new-authorized-value-label>`。"

#: ../../source/course_reserves.rst:28
msgid "You may also want to create new :ref:`item types <adding-item-types-label>`, `collection codes <#ccode>`__ and/or `shelving locations <#shelvelocvals>`__ to make it clear that the items are on reserve to your patrons. You will also want to be sure to confirm that your :ref:`circulation and fines rules <circulation-and-fines-rules-label>` are right for your new item types (whether they be hourly or daily loans)."
msgstr "您可能还需要创建新 :ref:`馆藏类型 <adding-item-types-label>`，`特藏代码 <#ccode>`__ 和/或 `书架位置 <#shelvelocvals>`__ ，以便读者使用。另外，您可能还需要定制 :ref:`流通和罚款规则 <circulation-and-fines-rules-label>` 以适用这些特殊文献（是基于小时还是天等）。"

#: ../../source/course_reserves.rst:38
msgid "Adding courses"
msgstr "新增课程"

#: ../../source/course_reserves.rst:40
msgid "Once you have completed your set up for course reserves you can start creating courses and adding titles to the reserve list."
msgstr "完成课程预留设置后，就可以开始创建需要预留的课程名称列表了。"

#: ../../source/course_reserves.rst:43
msgid "|image726|"
msgstr "|image726|"

